    "101 There are widespread strong signals of effort in the pharmaceutical industry to acquire, collaborate and scale up to develop more advanced AI-enabled protein engineering methods (such as InstaDeep, which raised $100m in 2022 102 before being acquired by BioNTech for $682m 103), with some proportion of efforts going to developing protein design tools.",
